      <title>C/C++练习</title>
      <link href="/2024/03/16/2024-3-16-C%E5%92%8CCpp/"/>
      <url>/2024/03/16/2024-3-16-C%E5%92%8CCpp/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="基础"><a href="#基础" class="headerlink" title="基础"></a>基础</h2><h4 id="第1道"><a href="#第1道" class="headerlink" title="第1道"></a>第1道</h4><p>```</p><h1 id="include"><a href="#include" class="headerlink" title="include "></a>include <stdio.h></h1><p>int main()<br>{<br>    int a = 20; int b = 4; int c = 2; int d = 1;<br>    printf(“a++=%d\n”, a++);<br>    printf(“a=%d\n”, a);<br>    printf(“++a=%d\n”, ++a);<br>    printf(“a=%d\n”, a);<br>    printf(“a—=%d\n”, a—);<br>    printf(“a=%d\n”, a);<br>    printf(“—a=%d\n”, —a);<br>    printf(“a=%d\n”, a);<br>    /<em>a后面++或—，这个表达式(如a++)的值不变，运行后的值(a)改变;<br>    a前面++或—，这个表达式的值和运行后的值均改变</em>/<br>    printf(“b-a/(c+2)=%d\n”, b - a / (c+2));<br>    //算术运算符中乘除优先于加减，括号最优先<br>    printf(“a/=b-c=%d\n”,a/=b-c);<br>    //复合赋值运算时先算=号右边<br>    printf(“a-b==c&gt;d=%d\n”, a - b == c &gt; d);<br>    //关系运算符中不等性比较(&gt;,&lt;,&gt;=,&lt;=)大于相等性比较(==,!=)<br>    //算术&gt;移位&gt;关系&gt;逻辑<br>    //碰到赋值(=)就先算右边<br>    return 0;<br>}<br>、、、<br><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-31%20160617.png" alt=""></p><h2 id="进阶"><a href="#进阶" class="headerlink" title="进阶"></a>进阶</h2><p>作者沉淀中</p><h2 id="挑战"><a href="#挑战" class="headerlink" title="挑战"></a>挑战</h2><p>作者沉淀中</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
