      <title>博客搭建心得</title>
      <link href="/2024/03/16/2024-3-16-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97/"/>
      <url>/2024/03/16/2024-3-16-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="博客声明"><a href="#博客声明" class="headerlink" title="博客声明"></a>博客声明</h2><ol><li>该博客使用Hexo框架和butterfly主题，在这里对两位开源大佬表示感谢</li><li>该博客会不定时更新美化</li><li>参考文献主要为Hexo官方文档和Butterfly主题教程</li><li>辅助参考文献为CSDN上诸位大佬的博文（因为较多就不挂链接）(不能保证他们是第一作者)</li></ol><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240320130309.jpg" alt=" "></p><h2 id="所需准备"><a href="#所需准备" class="headerlink" title="所需准备"></a>所需准备</h2><ol><li>电脑一台</li><li>计算机基础知识</li><li>至少70一年（用于购买服务器，域名，以及后续美化的核心——图床的核心——对象存储）(当然不用也可以，效果会差很多)</li><li>魔法（搭建会用到墙外网站）</li><li>年满18或监护人陪同（涉及到服务器，域名的注册以及后续的备案）</li><li>了解Markdown语法，用于博客的写作</li></ol><h2 id="开发环境"><a href="#开发环境" class="headerlink" title="开发环境"></a>开发环境</h2><ol><li><p><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">vscode</a></p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20134047.png" alt="vscode"></p><p>(若安装失败，尝试用管理员身份运行安装包)</p><ol><li><a href="https://www.runoob.com/git/git-install-setup.html">Git</a>          (需要魔法)</li></ol></li></ol><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20142040.png" alt="Git"></p><ul><li>配置环境变量</li></ul><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20150426.png" alt=" "></p><p>点击 编辑账户的环境变量</p><p>双击环境变量中的Path后新建，把Git安装包中cmd的安装目录粘贴进去，一直点确定</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20205856.png" alt=" "></p><ol><li><a href="https://nodejs.org/en">node.js</a></li></ol><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20151737.png" alt="node.js"></p><p>完成后是没有图标的，无需在意</p><ul><li><p>环境配置</p><ol><li><p>打开安装目录并新建 node_global    node_cache  两个文件夹</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20212300.png" alt=" "></p><ul><li>打开cmd输入npm config set prefix”你node_global文件的位置”</li></ul><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm<span class="built_in"> config </span><span class="built_in">set</span><span class="built_in"> prefix </span><span class="string">&quot;D:\node.js\node_global&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>打开cmd输入npm config set prefix“你node_cache文件的位置</li></ul><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="keyword">set</span> <span class="keyword">prefix</span><span class="string">&quot;D:<span class="subst">\n</span>ode.js<span class="subst">\n</span>ode_cache&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20220159.png" alt=" ">2. 设置环境变量<img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20150426.png" alt=" "></p><ul><li><p>点击 编辑账户的环境变量</p><p>双击环境变量中的Path后新建，把Git安装包中cmd的安装目录粘贴进去，一直点确定</p></li></ul></li></ol></li></ul><ol><li>Hexo</li></ol><p>打开安装好的git bash输入以下命令安装</p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-<span class="keyword">cli</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成后关闭</p><h2 id="粗略制作"><a href="#粗略制作" class="headerlink" title="粗略制作"></a>粗略制作</h2><ol><li>在c盘以外创建文件夹并更名</li></ol><p>如hexo-shue-blog，并记住路径</p><ol><li>在该文件下打开Git bash here,并输入以下命令，回车</li></ol><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">init</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20153957.png" alt=" "></p><p>这样就成功了，失败的话多试几次，这一堆文件夹的作用如下</p><ul><li>public 最终所见网页的所有内容</li><li>node_modules 插件及hexo所需的node.js模块</li><li>_config.yml 站点配置文件，设置一些公开信息</li><li>package.json 应用程序信息，配置hexo运行所需要的js包</li><li>scaffolds 模板文件夹，新建文章会默认包含对应模板内容</li><li>themes 存放主题文件，hexo根据主题生成速度很快的静态网页</li><li>source 用于存放用户资源 （除past文件夹，其余命名方式为“+ 文件夹”的文件被忽略</li></ul><ol><li>在Vscode中打开你blog所在的文件夹</li></ol><p>打开后如图</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-20%20115350.png" alt=" "></p><ol><li>打开终端输入以下命令并回车</li></ol><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">hexo s</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>点击第二个链接，一个简单的本地网页就制作成功了</li></ol><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20222601.png" alt=" "></p><p>在Terminal处同时按Ctrl和 c停止预览</p><h2 id="网页配置"><a href="#网页配置" class="headerlink" title="网页配置"></a>网页配置</h2><ol><li>打开vscode并打开博客文件输入命令</li></ol><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="keyword">clone</span> <span class="title">-b</span> <span class="keyword">master</span> <span class="title">https</span>://gitee.com/immyw/hexo-theme-butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​    等待安装完成</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20225021.png" alt=" "></p><p>将hexo-theme-butterfly粘贴到themes目录下</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20151408.png" alt=" "></p><ol><li>重新输入</li></ol><figure class="highlight mel"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-<span class="keyword">renderer</span>-pug hexo-<span class="keyword">renderer</span>-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-08%20230359.png" alt=" "></p><ol><li>hexo修改配置文件</li></ol><p>​            找到——config.yml文件，修改主题为hexo-theme-butterfly</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20152127.png" alt=" "></p><ol><li>本地预览</li></ol><figure class="highlight 1c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean  <span class="comment">//执行此命令后继续下一条</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo g  <span class="comment">//生成博客目录</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo s  <span class="comment">//本地预览</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建仓库"><a href="#创建仓库" class="headerlink" title="创建仓库"></a>创建仓库</h2><ol><li><p>打开 <a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a>并创建仓库(初次需要注册账号且该网站需要使用魔法)</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20152939.png" alt=" "></p></li></ol><p>2.仓库名称为你的名称.github.io     并勾选公开</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20153327.png" alt=" "></p><h2 id="配置密钥"><a href="#配置密钥" class="headerlink" title="配置密钥"></a>配置密钥</h2><ol><li>配置用户名和邮箱</li></ol><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config <span class="attr">--global</span> user<span class="selector-class">.name</span> <span class="string">&quot;xxx&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config <span class="attr">--globasl</span> user<span class="selector-class">.email</span> <span class="string">&quot;邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight excel"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -<span class="built_in">t</span> rsa -C <span class="string">&quot;邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20165055.png" alt=""></p><ol><li><p>进入所在文件目录</p><p>用记事本打开第二个并复制</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20165242.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>粘贴并创建</p></li></ol><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20165835.png" alt=""></p><ol><li>输入命令验证</li></ol><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">ssh</span> -T git<span class="variable">@github</span>.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​     输入 yes后若如下图则成功</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20170625.png" alt=""></p><h2 id="部署网站"><a href="#部署网站" class="headerlink" title="部署网站"></a>部署网站</h2><ol><li>链接到远程，添加仓库地址</li></ol><p>​      后三行改成图中样式，倒数第二行是你的仓库地址</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20215645.png" alt=""></p><ol><li>在网站本地根目录打开 git bash here 并依次执行以下命令</li></ol><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git <span class="comment">--save</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="购买配置"><a href="#购买配置" class="headerlink" title="购买配置"></a>购买配置</h2><ol><li>云服务器：购买个最便宜的就可以了，阿里等也可以</li></ol><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-09%20222355.png" alt=""></p><ol><li>购买域名：建议和服务器在一个公司购买，根据后缀和长短的不同，价钱也不同</li></ol><h2 id="DSN解析"><a href="#DSN解析" class="headerlink" title="DSN解析"></a>DSN解析</h2><ol><li>添加域名</li></ol><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-10%20122928.png" alt=""></p><ol><li>在腾讯云控制台添加两次解析记录</li></ol><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-10%20172037.png" alt=""></p><h2 id="远程连接"><a href="#远程连接" class="headerlink" title="远程连接"></a>远程连接</h2><ol><li>下载<a href="https://www.chiark.greenend.org.uk/~sgtatham/putty/latest.html">PUTTY</a></li></ol><ul><li><p>输入   root</p></li><li><p>输入密码（输的时候密码不可见）</p></li><li><p>输入  </p><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum <span class="keyword">install</span> git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>输入</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">adduser git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> 740 /etc/sudoers</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">vim /etc/sudoers</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>点击  i 键，找到彩色代码，在下面添加</li></ul><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git   <span class="keyword">All</span>=(<span class="keyword">ALL</span>)      <span class="keyword">ALL</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>按住Esc键并输入          :wq</p></li><li><p>输入</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> 400 /etc/sudoers</span><br><span class="line">sudo passwd git</span><br><span class="line">输入两次密码（不显示）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> ~/.ssh</span><br><span class="line">vim ~/.ssh/authorized_keys</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>将本地.ssh公钥粘贴进去</p></li><li><p>按住ESC       并输入      :wq</p></li><li><p>输入</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> 600 /home/git/.ssh/authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> 700 /home/git/.ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 本地git bash here中输入</p><figure class="highlight angelscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -v <span class="symbol">git@</span>服务器公网IP</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入密码</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">sudo su root</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /home/git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init <span class="comment">--bare blog.git</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chown</span> git:git -R blog.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog.git/hooks</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">vim post-receive</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#!/bin/bash</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="attribute">--work-tree</span>=/home/hexo <span class="attribute">--git-dir</span>=/home/git/blog.git checkout -f</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="完成配置"><a href="#完成配置" class="headerlink" title="完成配置"></a>完成配置</h2><ul><li><p>服务器</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">sudo su root</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> /www/repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chown</span> -R git:git /www/repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> -R 755 /www/repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> /www/hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chown</span> -R git:git /www/hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> -R 755 /www/hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /www/repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init <span class="comment">--bare hexo.git</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim <span class="regexp">/www/</span>repo<span class="regexp">/hexo.git/</span>hooks/post-recive</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按 i       输入以下代码</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chown -r git:git <span class="regexp">/www/</span>repo<span class="regexp">/hexo.git/</span>hooks/post-receive</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod +x <span class="regexp">/www/</span>repo<span class="regexp">/hexo.git/</span>hooks/post-receive</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在服务器上安装宝塔面板</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -<span class="keyword">y</span> wget &amp;&amp; wget -O install.<span class="keyword">sh</span> https://download.bt.<span class="keyword">cn</span>/install/install_6.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="keyword">sh</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">sh</span> install.<span class="keyword">sh</span> ed8484bec</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入y继续，等到账号密码生成，记住</p><p>放行8888端口</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-10%20180935.png" alt=""></p><p>在浏览器上打开外网访问地址，登录</p><p>进入宝塔里的软件商店，将LNMP一键安装</p><p>创建站点</p><p><img src="https://typora678-1324881552.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202024-03-10%20201959.png" alt=""></p><h2 id="配置修改"><a href="#配置修改" class="headerlink" title="配置修改"></a>配置修改</h2><p>将倒数第二行进行修改</p><p><img src="C:\Users\qq335\Pictures\Screenshots\屏幕截图 2024-03-10 211620.png" alt=""></p><p>打开putty工具，连接后</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chown</span> -R git:git /www/repo/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chown</span> -R git:git /www/hexo/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>本地根目录打开 git bash here执行</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">hexo clean</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">hexo d -g</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="备案后续"><a href="#备案后续" class="headerlink" title="备案后续"></a>备案后续</h2><p>将下面代码粘贴在footer,建议在户籍地备案，否则可能需要提供暂住证</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img <span class="attribute">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://haiyong.site/img/icp.png&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;a <span class="attribute">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://beian.mps.gov.cn/#/query/webSearch?code=41120202000337&quot;</span> <span class="attribute">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;noreferrer&quot;</span> <span class="attribute">target</span>=<span class="string">&quot;_blank&quot;</span>&gt;你的备案号&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="其他相关"><a href="#其他相关" class="headerlink" title="其他相关"></a>其他相关</h2><ol><li>网站美化网上有很多教程，由于牵扯的东西较多，这里不作阐述</li><li>图床使用的是picgo加腾讯云对象存储</li><li>Markdown写作使用的是typora</li><li>如果有空还是要进行icp备案和公安备案的，好处就不多说了</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
